  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). Comprehensive mesh independence studies, iterative convergence checks, and a structured validation campaign against in vitro hemolysis data across five flow-speed operating points collectively support the Medium assurance declaration. The overall evidence body is considered sufficient for regulatory submission at MRL 2.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/morrison-cpb-cfd-hemolysis-v3",
