      "name": "Pump hydraulic performance validation — pressure-flow curves",
      "description": "Predicted pressure rise and shaft torque were validated against experimental measurements at three rotational speeds. Discrepancies remained below 5% across the operating range, confirming adequate fidelity of the turbomachinery flow field for hemolysis sensitivity analysis."
    }
  ],
